text: "Molnljus" is a Swedish language song by singer William Stridh. The song was performed for the first time in Melodifestivalen 2020. The song was written by Christian Holmström, David Kreuger, Markus Lidén and Stridh himself. It was produced by Holmström, Lidén and Kreuger.
